title: a / b / .. / d
pid: eceaed3f-c287-4bb6-a05e-160d10a13a4f
body: |2-
  In Tantivy, find everything matching a, b and d.
  In TypeDB, walk up containerward from each match to d
  until finding a match to b.
  Discard any d that don't reach a match to b.
  For those that do, search containerward from each match of b
  to see if any of those are contained by something matching a.
  Return everything that does.
